---
title: "Formal Specification of the Lateralus Bytecode VM"
author: bad-antics
date: 2026-04-06
abstract: This document provides a formal specification of the Lateralus bytecode VM, including instruction encoding, stack semantics, operand types, and operational semantics. We discuss the tradeoffs in our design decisions and provide examples to illustrate key concepts.

